snippet.title: Note Series:Amber|My Top 13 Amber Fragrances|Perfume Collection 2021
snippet.description:
Hey Everyone!  

Welcome to or welcome back to my channel, Opinionated Scents. My name is TeraMichelle. This is our safe space to discuss all things Fragrance, whether we like them or not. 

Today, we are discussing my Top 13 Favorite Amber Fragrances. Be sure to leave your favorite in the comments. I hope you enjoy the video. 

Fragrances Mentioned:

Gentle Fluidity Gold by MFK
Amberlicious by Dua
Your Wish is My Command by Dua
Alien Essence Absolu by Mugler
Marc Jacob's Daisy Love Daze
Paris Hilton in Paris
Symbol Royal
Casablanca
Kayali Invite Only Amber 23
Narciso Rodriguez Narciso Ambre
Kayali Vanilla 28
Si Le Parfum by Giorgio Armani
L'ambre Des Mervielles by Hermes

Popular Videos:

It's Another Haul Ya'll: https://youtu.be/EKpuQrNwhAk
